This produces a 'filtered [item]' with value 30. If you have two such items, filter both, then combine them to get a value of 60. Using 'vial' on a solid item creates an 'extract' (value 30). Filtering an 'extract' creates a 'poorly-filtered extract' (value 10). Combining a 'filtered [item]' with a 'poorly-filtered extract' of the same type (magical/mundane) yields 40. Combining higher value items further often *reduces* their value, so aim for two distinct filtered items and combine them once.
